entry.title: novitechie/jetbra
entry.summary:
Jetbra

An activation tool for jetbrains family products,including plugins

Notice

More than 30% of this project was copied from ja-netfilter, please refer to ja-netfilter for more details So for users using ja-netfilter, there is no need to install this. you just need add the following configuration to the results section of power.conf to use the activation code generated by this project

EQUAL,,65537,->

Usage

  1. Download jetbra-all.zip from the release page and unzip it
  2. Execute installation script macOS or Linux: execute "scripts/install.sh"
    Windows: double click to execute "scripts\install-current-user.vbs" (For current user),"scripts\install-all-users.vbs" (For all users)
  3. Log in again to load environment variables
  4. copy the activation code below and activate the software
K5EIF58U2M---

For plugins, it is impossible for me to generate an activation code for each paid plugin, so I developed an tampermonkey script. You only need to install this script to generate an activation code by clicking on the plugin homepage.
